## Code Example Usage

### When to Use PRD Code Examples

**PRD contains**:

- Data model TypeScript types
- UI component structures
- Loading/error state examples
- Layout specifications

**Example**:

```typescript
// PRD Section 8.1: Data Models
// Copy this EXACTLY into your implementation
type Project = {
  id: string
  name: string
  description: string | null
  status: "active" | "archived" | "deleted"
  created_at: string
  updated_at: string
}
```

### When to Use ADR Code Examples

**ADRs contain**:

- Architectural patterns
- Configuration setups
- Best practice implementations
- Reusable code templates

**Example**:

```typescript
// ADR-005: React Query Configuration
// Use this pattern for ALL queries
const queryConfig = {
  staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000, // From ADR
  cacheTime: 10 * 60 * 1000, // From ADR
  refetchOnWindowFocus: false, // From ADR
  retry: 1, // From ADR
}
```

