## Validation Rules

### PRD Compliance Check

Before marking task complete:

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria**: ALL items implemented (not partial)
- [ ] **Technical Specs**: Components match specified names
- [ ] **Data Models**: TypeScript types match PRD exactly
- [ ] **Success Metrics**: Performance targets achievable
- [ ] **User Story**: Feature solves stated user problem

### ADR Compliance Check

Before marking task complete:

- [ ] **Naming**: Follows ADR-004 conventions
- [ ] **Routes**: Follows ADR-006 structure
- [ ] **Data Fetching**: Follows ADR-002, ADR-005
- [ ] **State**: Follows ADR-007 (React Query + Zustand)
- [ ] **Errors**: Follows ADR-008 (3-layer pattern)
- [ ] **Code Style**: Matches ADR examples

