## Common Mistakes to Avoid

### ❌ Mistake 1: Partial Implementation

**Wrong**:

```typescript
// Only implementing 2 out of 5 acceptance criteria
<ProjectInfoCard>
  <h2>{project.name}</h2>
  {/* Missing: description, status, created_at */}
</ProjectInfoCard>
```

**Correct**:

```typescript
// Implement ALL acceptance criteria from PRD
<ProjectInfoCard>
  <h2>{project.name}</h2>
  <Badge>{project.status}</Badge>  {/* ✅ From criteria */}
  <p>{project.description}</p>     {/* ✅ From criteria */}
  <span>{formatDate(project.created_at)}</span>  {/* ✅ From criteria */}
</ProjectInfoCard>
```

### ❌ Mistake 2: Ignoring ADR Patterns

**Wrong**:

```typescript
// Custom query configuration (ignores ADR-005)
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: ["myCustomKey"],
  staleTime: 0, // Not following ADR
})
```

**Correct**:

```typescript
// Follow ADR-005 pattern exactly
const { data } = useProject(projectId, {
  staleTime: 5 * 60 * 1000, // From ADR-005
})
```

### ❌ Mistake 3: Wrong File Location

**Wrong**:

```
src/components/OverviewPage.tsx  // Not following ADR-004
```

**Correct**:

```
src/features/workspace/components/project-detail/overview/OverviewPage.tsx
// Follows ADR-004: Feature-based grouping
```

