## Troubleshooting

### If Confused During Implementation

**Question**: "What should this component do?"
→ **Answer**: Check PRD Section 4 (Feature Requirements) → Find feature → Read Acceptance Criteria

**Question**: "How should I name this file?"
→ **Answer**: Check ADR-004 (Component Naming) → Apply feature-based grouping pattern

**Question**: "How should I fetch this data?"
→ **Answer**: Check ADR-002 (Lazy Loading) + ADR-005 (React Query) → Apply patterns

**Question**: "What TypeScript type should I use?"
→ **Answer**: Check PRD Section 8 (Data Requirements) → Copy exact type definition

**Question**: "How do I handle this error?"
→ **Answer**: Check ADR-008 (Error Handling) → Apply 3-layer pattern

